metadata.name: Broken Bridges
metadata.description:
Broken bridges üåÅ 
This piece was created to have great meaning behind what you see  
As life is short things begin to age and time slips away.  
Cherish the time you have and enjoy everyday counting the sunrises as everything eventually comes to a end.  
Remember that life is too short to worry about broken bridges, so move forward and build a bridge of dreams and courage.
